          "reviewBody": "🔴Daycare is not for dependent kids, kids below 4 yr\n-M sharing my 1st hand experience\n-they don't have staff 11 am to 1 pm\n-1 teacher manages playarea kids\n-1 teacher manages lunch time kids and daycare area (15 to 20+ kids ) at a time, she serves food and she sees who eats or not and same teacher helps to eat (seems sm superman)\nYour kid is free to eat from anyones plate, they r free to eat everything lying on the floor, pressed through everyone's footstep\n-1 maushi changes cloths of everyone, she refill everyone's bag with their things, she take cares if anyone want to go to washroom, she washes everyone's hands ,she picks N drops kids from entrance (again a superman)\nBut if ur child wants to go to WASHROOM N he or she is saying it again and again then SORRY but no one is their to listen to him/her between 12 to 1 pm because kids to b handled are 28+ kids .\n-And if 1 of 3 managers are on leave then it's a SABJI MANDI\ninfact full daycare management is on AUTO mode between 12 to 1\n\nPathetic N worst management ever",
